                <table width="760" border="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td width="40" align="right" valign="top"><p><img src="../../../help/help/images/bullet.gif" width="16" height="10"></p></td>
                    <td width="545" valign="top"><p> Players who are at least 30 days old can apply to become a Secret Agent. This is a big responsibility&mdash;an important part of your job is to help keep Club Penguin safe. To apply, click o n the &ldquo;M&rdquo; located at the top right corner of your screen. Click &ldquo;Become a Secret Agent&rdquo; and take the quiz.</p></td>
